  "description": "Freeze engaged (opal_freeze=0.85) on a 600ms Gaussian window grain with freezeSize=0.08 — only 8% of the 4-second buffer is accessible. The granulator orbits a microscopically small sonic territory, cycling through the same 0.32-second frozen snapshot endlessly. At density=25, 300 grains/second total arrive from 12 voices. Deep filter at 800Hz seals it below the thermocline. Hadal zone: extreme pressure, total isolation.",
